casebody.data:
William D. Shipman, et al., Respondents, v. The Engleton Manufacturing Co., Appellant. Decided July 2, 1886. Appeal by defendant from order of reference to hear and determine. John E. Parsons, for appellant. Thomas Hunt, for respondents.

Before Truax and Ingraham, JJ.

Opinion

Per Curiam.

Order reversed, with $10 costs and disbursements, and motion to refer denied.
